creator: CMPL
descriptionHtml:
This app is for use by Community Health Initiative workers of Impact India Foundation to enter details of beneficiaries and work done in Janani, Yuva and Bal Swasthya programs, serving rural populations in different parts of Maharashtra.

The app aims to improve productivity of the team as well as ensure constant tracking of Key Performance Indicators (KPIs) of the projects, so as to ensure that maximum benefit is derived from the projects by the targeted rural population.
